# Project Manager

## Overview
Plans and executes blockchain projects, ensuring timely delivery and stakeholder alignment.

## Key Responsibilities
- Create detailed project plans and timelines.
- Coordinate tasks and resources across teams.
- Track progress and mitigate risks.

## Required Skills
- Project management tools and methodologies.
- Cross-functional communication.
- Problem-solving and adaptability.

## Example Tasks
- Run sprint planning meetings.
- Track milestones and deliverables.
- Prepare project status reports for leadership.